metadata.name: ILLUSION
metadata.description:
She thinks she's smarter than everyone! Is this dirty girl going to be able to trick me?! How so?! Even the lie detector speaks in her favor, and this fortuneteller is also probably a charlatan ..!
Old man, go relax and drink something strong, you are not your own at all .. Relax, each thread has its own end and it can be found for anyone .. And now the end has come ..
An examination came that it was not her, but there were other clues where they found fingerprints at the crime scene .. It seems some kind of Katie,very much resembles your mistress according to the description of the old man ..
